# Puchi Backend

Monorepo Go microservices với **Kratos v3**. 7 service modules trong `app/`, workspace qua `go.work`.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Ngôn ngữ | Go 1.26 |
| Framework | Kratos v3 (HTTP/gRPC hybrid, Protobuf-first) |
| DI | Wire (compile-time) |
| Auth | Zitadel (self-host) — JWT verification qua JWKS |
| Auth middleware | `pkg/auth/` (shared across services, JWT middleware verify signature + issuer) |
| Database | PostgreSQL 18 (CloudNativePG) |
| Cache | Valkey/Redis |
| Message Queue | NATS (event-driven) |
| Object Storage | Garage (S3 API) |
| Migration | goose |

## Cấu trúc monorepo

```
puchi-backend/
├── api/                           # Protobuf definitions CHUNG
│   ├── auth/v1/
│   ├── content/v1/
│   └── ...
├── app/                           # 7 Go service modules
│   ├── core/                      # Auth verify + User + Game (Phase 1)
│   ├── content/                   # Courses, units, lessons
│   ├── grading/                   # Dictation, listening grading
│   ├── user/                      # Profile, settings (Phase 3)
│   ├── game/                      # XP, leaderboard (Phase 3)
│   ├── media/                     # Upload, resize (Phase 1)
│   └── notification/              # Push, email (Phase 3)
├── pkg/                           # Shared Kit library (includes pkg/auth/ for JWT auth middleware)
├── go.work                        # Go workspace (dev only)
└── Makefile                       # Build helper
```

## Quy tắc layered architecture (Kratos)

```
internal/
├── service/       # Transport layer - proto server impl, validate input
├── biz/           # Domain logic - usecases, entities, repo interfaces
└── data/          # Data layer - repository implementations (DB, cache)
```

**Dependency rule:** `service -> biz -> data` (biz không import data)

## Auth middleware

Auth middleware nằm trong `pkg/auth/` (shared across services), gồm:

| File | Mô tả |
|------|-------|
| `auth.go` | Khởi tạo JWTValidator từ config |
| `jwt.go` | JWTValidator — fetch JWKS từ Zitadel, verify signature + issuer |
| `middleware.go` | HTTP middleware — parse JWT từ `Authorization` header, inject UserID vào context |
| `context.go` | `UserIDFromContext()` / `NewContextWithUserID()` |
| `sync.go` | Lazy user sync — tạo user trong DB từ JWT claims |

JWT verification flow:
```
Request → Authorization: Bearer <JWT>
       → JWTValidator.ParseAndValidate()
       → Fetch JWKS từ https://auth.puchi.io.vn/oauth/v2/keys (cached 15 phút)
       → Verify signature + issuer claim
       → Extract sub (userID) + email → inject context
```

## CI/CD

- **CI**: GitHub Actions (`backend.yml`) — Matrix build 7 services, Go 1.26
- **Paths trigger**: `app/**`, `api/**`, `pkg/**`
- **Docker**: Mỗi service có Dockerfile riêng (Go 1.26 builder → debian slim runner)
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-{service}`
- **Ports**: HTTP 8000, gRPC 9000

## Dockerfile pattern

```dockerfile
FROM golang:1.26 AS builder
WORKDIR /src
COPY go.mod go.sum ./
RUN go mod download
COPY . .
RUN go mod tidy && go build -o /bin/{service} ./cmd/{service}/

FROM debian:stable-slim
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    ca-certificates netbase && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
COPY --from=builder /bin/{service} /app/{service}
WORKDIR /app
EXPOSE 8000 9000
CMD ["./{service}", "-conf", "/data/conf"]
```

## Kết nối Infra

| Service | Internal DNS |
|---------|--------------|
| PostgreSQL (Puchi) | `pg-puchi-rw.puchi-db.svc.cluster.local:5432` |
| NATS | `nats.platform.svc.cluster.local:4222` |
| Garage (S3) | `http://garage.platform.svc.cluster.local:3900` |
| Valkey/Redis | `valkey-node.platform.svc.cluster.local:6379` |
| Zitadel | `zitadel.puchi-auth.svc.cluster.local:8080` |
| Zitadel JWKS | `https://auth.puchi.io.vn/oauth/v2/keys` |

